data.description: COMING SOON! Welcome to this beautifully renovated double-wide mobile home.  Enjoy the tranquility of nature with your home nestled on a spacious half-acre lot in beautiful Forest Hill.  Unwind, relax and enjoy the views sitting on your deck.  As you enter your new home you will be amazed with the open space, which makes it a great entertaining space.  Indulge your inner chef in this gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinet and counterspace.  All new vinyl plank flooring and windows throughout.  Both bathrooms have been fully renovated.  There is a slider from the kitchen that will lead to   endless possibilities for your fully fenced backyard.  Make your appointment today!
